Plot a generated 3D PCA loading plot in RStudio

Source: R/metabolomics_plots.R
met.print_PCA3DLoading.Rd

met.print_PCA3DLoading opens a new graphics device to show the generated 3D PCA loading plot.

Usage

met.print_PCA3DLoading(mSetObj = NA)

Arguments

mSetObj

Input name of the created mSet object. Data container after met.plot_PCA3DLoading.

Value

A 3D scatter plot. To close the graphics device, execute rgl::close3d().
